summary: This is a deposit slip from Municipal Credit Union showing a deposit of $7,912.53 into a primary share account at the Oceanside Branch, bringing the new balance to $8,413.53. The document indicates a hold on part of the funds due to a large deposit.

events.title: Bank Deposit
events.description: A deposit of $7,912.53 was made to a primary share account at Municipal Credit Union's Oceanside Branch, consisting of two checks totaling $7,912.53.

locations: Municipal Credit Union Oceanside Branch, 3411 Long Beach Road, Oceanside, NY 11572
keyFacts: A financial transaction occurred on July 22, 2019, involving a deposit of $7,912.53.
The deposit was made at the Municipal Credit Union Oceanside Branch in New York.
The deposit consisted of two checks: one for $5,731.58 and another for $2,180.95.
Part of the deposited funds ($2,912.53) was subject to a hold until July 30, 2019, due to being a 'Large Deposit'.
The document is a routine bank record with no direct mention of individuals or entities related to the Epstein case.
